Package de.weltraumschaf.ebnf.ast.nodes Description

All available AST nodes.

This package is a part of the open-source EBNF library

This package contains all available nodes an EBNF AST may have.

The nodes are dived in three types:

  1. Leafs: The nodes Identifier, Terminal, and Null are leafs. They can not contain other nodes as children.
  2. Composites: All other nodes are composite nodes and may have one or more child nodes.
  3. Special: The leaf node Null is a special purpose node mostly used in the unit tests. It is used as default parent node for all composite nodes.
